48bool AchievementCriteriaData::IsValid(AchievementCriteria const* criteria)
49{
50 if (dataType >= MAX_ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE)
51 {
52 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` for criteria (Entry: %u) has wrong data type (%u), ignored.", criteria->ID, dataType);
53 return false;
54 }
55
56 switch (criteria->Entry->Type)
57 {
58 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KILL_CREATURE:
59 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KILL_CREATURE_TYPE:
60 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_BG:
61 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_FALL_WITHOUT_DYING:
62 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_QUEST: // only hardcoded list
63 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CAST_SPELL:
64 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_RATED_ARENA:
65 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DO_EMOTE:
66 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_SPECIAL_PVP_KILL:
67 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_DUEL:
68 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LOOT_TYPE:
69 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CAST_SPELL2:
70 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BE_SPELL_TARGET:
71 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BE_SPELL_TARGET2:
72 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EQUIP_EPIC_ITEM:
73 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_NEED_ON_LOOT:
74 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_GREED_ON_LOOT:
75 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BG_OBJECTIVE_CAPTURE:
76 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HONORABLE_KILL:
77 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_DAILY_QUEST: // only Children's Week achievements
78 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_USE_ITEM: // only Children's Week achievements
79 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_GET_KILLING_BLOWS:
80 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_REACH_LEVEL:
81 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ON_LOGIN:
82 break;
83 default:
84 if (dataType != ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_SCRIPT)
85 {
86 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` has data for non-supported criteria type (Entry: %u Type: %u), ignored.", criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type);
87 return false;
88 }
89 break;
90 }
91
92 switch (dataType)
93 {
94 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_NONE:
95 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_INSTANCE_SCRIPT:
96 return true;
97 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_CREATURE:
98 if (!creature.id || !sObjectMgr->GetCreatureTemplate(creature.id))
99 {
100 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_CREATURE (%u) has non-existing creature id in value1 (%u), ignored.",
101 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, creature.id);
102 return false;
103 }
104 return true;
105 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE:
106 if (!classRace.class_id && !classRace.race_id)
107 {
108 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE (%u) must not have 0 in either value field, ignored.",
109 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType);
110 return false;
111 }
112 if (classRace.class_id && ((1 << (classRace.class_id-1)) & CLASSMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE) == 0)
113 {
114 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE (%u) has non-existing class in value1 (%u), ignored.",
115 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, classRace.class_id);
116 return false;
117 }
118 if (classRace.race_id && ((1 << (classRace.race_id-1)) & RACEMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE) == 0)
119 {
120 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE (%u) has non-existing race in value2 (%u), ignored.",
121 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, classRace.race_id);
122 return false;
123 }
124 return true;
125 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_PLAYER_LESS_HEALTH:
126 if (health.percent < 1 || health.percent > 100)
127 {
128 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_PLAYER_LESS_HEALTH (%u) has wrong percent value in value1 (%u), ignored.",
129 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, health.percent);
130 return false;
131 }
132 return true;
133 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA:
134 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_AURA:
135 {
136 SpellInfo const* spellEntry = sSpellMgr->GetSpellInfo(aura.spell_id);
137 if (!spellEntry)
138 {
139 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type %s (%u) has wrong spell id in value1 (%u), ignored.",
140 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, (dataType == ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA ? "ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA" : "ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_AURA"), dataType, aura.spell_id);
141 return false;
142 }
143 SpellEffectInfo const* effect = spellEntry->GetEffect(DIFFICULTY_NONE, aura.effect_idx);
144 if (!effect)
145 {
146 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type %s (%u) has wrong spell effect index in value2 (%u), ignored.",
147 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, (dataType == ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA ? "ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA" : "ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_AURA"), dataType, aura.effect_idx);
148 return false;
149 }
150 if (!effect->ApplyAuraName)
151 {
152 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type %s (%u) has non-aura spell effect (ID: %u Effect: %u), ignores.",
153 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, (dataType == ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA ? "ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA" : "ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_AURA"), dataType, aura.spell_id, aura.effect_idx);
154 return false;
155 }
156 return true;
157 }
158 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_VALUE:
159 if (value.compType >= COMP_TYPE_MAX)
160 {
161 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_VALUE (%u) has wrong ComparisionType in value2 (%u), ignored.",
162 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, value.compType);
163 return false;
164 }
165 return true;
166 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_LEVEL:
167 if (level.minlevel > STRONG_MAX_LEVEL)
168 {
169 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_LEVEL (%u) has wrong minlevel in value1 (%u), ignored.",
170 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, level.minlevel);
171 return false;
172 }
173 return true;
174 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_GENDER:
175 if (gender.gender > GENDER_NONE)
176 {
177 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_GENDER (%u) has wrong gender in value1 (%u), ignored.",
178 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, gender.gender);
179 return false;
180 }
181 return true;
182 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_SCRIPT:
183 if (!ScriptId)
184 {
185 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_SCRIPT (%u) does not have ScriptName set, ignored.",
186 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType);
187 return false;
188 }
189 return true;
190 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_MAP_PLAYER_COUNT:
191 if (map_players.maxcount <= 0)
192 {
193 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_MAP_PLAYER_COUNT (%u) has wrong max players count in value1 (%u), ignored.",
194 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, map_players.maxcount);
195 return false;
196 }
197 return true;
198 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_TEAM:
199 if (team.team != ALLIANCE && team.team != HORDE)
200 {
201 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_TEAM (%u) has unknown team in value1 (%u), ignored.",
202 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, team.team);
203 return false;
204 }
205 return true;
206 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_DRUNK:
207 if (drunk.state >= MAX_DRUNKEN)
208 {
209 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_DRUNK (%u) has unknown drunken state in value1 (%u), ignored.",
210 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, drunk.state);
211 return false;
212 }
213 return true;
214 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_HOLIDAY:
215 if (!sHolidaysStore.LookupEntry(holiday.id))
216 {
217 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_HOLIDAY (%u) has unknown holiday in value1 (%u), ignored.",
218 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, holiday.id);
219 return false;
220 }
221 return true;
222 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_GAME_EVENT:
223 {
224 GameEventMgr::GameEventDataMap const& events = sGameEventMgr->GetEventMap();
225 if (game_event.id < 1 || game_event.id >= events.size())
226 {
227 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_GAME_EVENT (%u) has unknown game_event in value1 (%u), ignored.",
228 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, game_event.id);
229 return false;
230 }
231 return true;
232 }
233 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_BG_LOSS_TEAM_SCORE:
234 return true; // not check correctness node indexes
235 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_EQUIPED_ITEM:
236 if (equipped_item.item_quality >= MAX_ITEM_QUALITY)
237 {
238 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_EQUIPED_ITEM (%u) has unknown quality state in value1 (%u), ignored.",
239 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, equipped_item.item_quality);
240 return false;
241 }
242 return true;
243 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE:
244 if (!classRace.class_id && !classRace.race_id)
245 {
246 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE (%u) must not have 0 in either value field, ignored.",
247 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType);
248 return false;
249 }
250 if (classRace.class_id && ((1 << (classRace.class_id-1)) & CLASSMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE) == 0)
251 {
252 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE (%u) has non-existing class in value1 (%u), ignored.",
253 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, classRace.class_id);
254 return false;
255 }
256 if (classRace.race_id && ((1 << (classRace.race_id-1)) & RACEMASK_ALL_PLAYABLE) == 0)
257 {
258 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE (%u) has non-existing race in value2 (%u), ignored.",
259 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, classRace.race_id);
260 return false;
261 }
262 return true;
263 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_KNOWN_TITLE:
264 if (!sCharTitlesStore.LookupEntry(known_title.title_id))
265 {
266 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) for data type ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_KNOWN_TITLE (%u) have unknown title_id in value1 (%u), ignore.",
267 criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType, known_title.title_id);
268 return false;
269 }
270 return true;
271 default:
272 TC_LOG_ERROR("sql.sql", "Table `achievement_criteria_data` (Entry: %u Type: %u) has data for non-supported data type (%u), ignored.", criteria->ID, criteria->Entry->Type, dataType);
273 return false;
274 }
275}

277bool AchievementCriteriaData::Meets(uint32 criteria_id, Player const* source, Unit const* target, uint32 miscValue1 /*= 0*/) const
278{
279 switch (dataType)
280 {
281 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_NONE:
282 return true;
283 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_CREATURE:
284 if (!target || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_UNIT)
285 return false;
286 return target->GetEntry() == creature.id;
287 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE:
288 if (!target || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
289 return false;
290 if (classRace.class_id && classRace.class_id != target->ToPlayer()->getClass())
291 return false;
292 if (classRace.race_id && classRace.race_id != target->ToPlayer()->getRace())
293 return false;
294 return true;
295 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_PLAYER_CLASS_RACE:
296 if (source->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
297 return false;
298 if (classRace.class_id && classRace.class_id != source->ToPlayer()->getClass())
299 return false;
300 if (classRace.race_id && classRace.race_id != source->ToPlayer()->getRace())
301 return false;
302 return true;
303 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_PLAYER_LESS_HEALTH:
304 if (!target || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
305 return false;
306 return !target->HealthAbovePct(health.percent);
307 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_AURA:
308 return source->HasAuraEffect(aura.spell_id, aura.effect_idx);
309 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_AURA:
310 return target && target->HasAuraEffect(aura.spell_id, aura.effect_idx);
311 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_VALUE:
312 return CompareValues(ComparisionType(value.compType), miscValue1, value.value);
313 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_LEVEL:
314 if (!target)
315 return false;
316 return target->getLevel() >= level.minlevel;
317 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_GENDER:
318 if (!target)
319 return false;
320 return target->getGender() == gender.gender;
321 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_SCRIPT:
322 return sScriptMgr->OnCriteriaCheck(ScriptId, const_cast<Player*>(source), const_cast<Unit*>(target));
323 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_MAP_PLAYER_COUNT:
324 return source->GetMap()->GetPlayersCountExceptGMs() <= map_players.maxcount;
325 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_T_TEAM:
326 if (!target || target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
327 return false;
328 return target->ToPlayer()->GetTeam() == team.team;
329 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_DRUNK:
330 return Player::GetDrunkenstateByValue(source->GetDrunkValue()) >= DrunkenState(drunk.state);
331 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_HOLIDAY:
332 return IsHolidayActive(HolidayIds(holiday.id));
333 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_GAME_EVENT:
334 return IsEventActive(game_event.id);
335 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_BG_LOSS_TEAM_SCORE:
336 {
337 Battleground* bg = source->GetBattleground();
338 if (!bg)
339 return false;
340
341 uint32 score = bg->GetTeamScore(source->GetTeamId() == TEAM_ALLIANCE ? TEAM_HORDE : TEAM_ALLIANCE);
342 return score >= bg_loss_team_score.min_score && score <= bg_loss_team_score.max_score;
343 }
344 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_INSTANCE_SCRIPT:
345 {
346 if (!source->IsInWorld())
347 return false;
348 Map* map = source->GetMap();
349 if (!map->IsDungeon())
350 {
351 TC_LOG_ERROR("achievement", "Achievement system call ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_INSTANCE_SCRIPT (%u) for achievement criteria %u for non-dungeon/non-raid map %u",
352 dataType, criteria_id, map->GetId());
353 return false;
354 }
355 InstanceScript* instance = map->ToInstanceMap()->GetInstanceScript();
356 if (!instance)
357 {
358 TC_LOG_ERROR("achievement", "Achievement system call ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_INSTANCE_SCRIPT (%u) for achievement criteria %u for map %u but map does not have a instance script",
359 dataType, criteria_id, map->GetId());
360 return false;
361 }
362 return instance->CheckAchievementCriteriaMeet(criteria_id, source, target, miscValue1);
363 }
364 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_EQUIPED_ITEM:
365 {
366 ItemTemplate const* pProto = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(miscValue1);
367 if (!pProto)
368 return false;
369 return pProto->GetBaseItemLevel() >= equipped_item.item_level && pProto->GetQuality() >= equipped_item.item_quality;
370 }
371 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_MAP_ID:
372 return source->GetMapId() == map_id.mapId;
373 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_DATA_TYPE_S_KNOWN_TITLE:
374 {
375 if (CharTitlesEntry const* titleInfo = sCharTitlesStore.LookupEntry(known_title.title_id))
376 return source && source->HasTitle(titleInfo->MaskID);
377
378 return false;
379 }
380 default:
381 break;
382 }
383 return false;
384}
385
386bool AchievementCriteriaDataSet::Meets(Player const* source, Unit const* target, uint32 miscValue /*= 0*/) const
387{
388 for (AchievementCriteriaData const& data : storage)
389 if (!data.Meets(criteria_id, source, target, miscValue))
390 return false;
391
392 return true;
393}

416template<class T>
417void AchievementMgr<T>::RemoveCriteriaProgress(AchievementCriteria const* entry)
418{
419 if (!entry)
420 return;
421
422 CriteriaProgressMap::iterator criteriaProgress = m_criteriaProgress.find(entry->ID);
423 if (criteriaProgress == m_criteriaProgress.end())
424 return;
425
426 WorldPackets::Achievement::CriteriaDeleted criteriaDeleted;
427 criteriaDeleted.CriteriaID = entry->ID;
428 SendPacket(criteriaDeleted.Write());
429
430 m_criteriaProgress.erase(criteriaProgress);
431}
432
433template<>
434void AchievementMgr<Guild>::RemoveCriteriaProgress(AchievementCriteria const* entry)
435{
436 if (!entry)
437 return;
438
439 CriteriaProgressMap::iterator criteriaProgress = m_criteriaProgress.find(entry->ID);
440 if (criteriaProgress == m_criteriaProgress.end())
441 return;
442
443 WorldPackets::Achievement::GuildCriteriaDeleted guildCriteriaDeleted;
444 guildCriteriaDeleted.GuildGUID = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
445 guildCriteriaDeleted.CriteriaID = entry->ID;
446 SendPacket(guildCriteriaDeleted.Write());
447
448 m_criteriaProgress.erase(criteriaProgress);
449}

451template<class T>
452void AchievementMgr<T>::ResetAchievementCriteria(AchievementCriteriaTypes type, uint64 miscValue1, uint64 miscValue2, bool evenIfCriteriaComplete)
453{
454 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "ResetAchievementCriteria(%u, " UI64FMTD ", " UI64FMTD ")", type, miscValue1, miscValue2);
455
456 // disable for gamemasters with GM-mode enabled
457 if (GetOwner()->IsGameMaster())
458 return;
459
460 AchievementCriteriaList const& achievementCriteriaList = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaByType(type);
461 for (AchievementCriteria const* achievementCriteria : achievementCriteriaList)
462 {
463 if (achievementCriteria->Entry->FailEvent != miscValue1 || (achievementCriteria->Entry->FailAsset && achievementCriteria->Entry->FailAsset != miscValue2))
464 continue;
465
466 AchievementCriteriaTreeList const* trees = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaTreesByCriteria(achievementCriteria->ID);
467 bool allComplete = true;
468 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : *trees)
469 {
470 // don't update already completed criteria if not forced or achievement already complete
471 if (!(IsCompletedCriteriaTree(tree) && !evenIfCriteriaComplete) || !HasAchieved(tree->Achievement->ID))
472 {
473 allComplete = false;
474 break;
475 }
476 }
477
478 if (allComplete)
479 continue;
480
481 RemoveCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria);
482 }
483}

488 // Not needed
489}

496template<>
497void AchievementMgr<Player>::DeleteFromDB(ObjectGuid guid)
498{

528template<class T>
529void AchievementMgr<T>::SaveToDB(SQLTransaction& /*trans*/)
530{
531}
532template<>
533void AchievementMgr<Player>::SaveToDB(SQLTransaction& trans)
534{
535 if (!m_completedAchievements.empty())
536 {
537 for (CompletedAchievementMap::iterator iter = m_completedAchievements.begin(); iter != m_completedAchievements.end(); ++iter)
538 {
539 if (!iter->second.changed)
540 continue;
541
542 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_ACHIEVEMENT_BY_ACHIEVEMENT);
543 stmt->setUInt16(0, iter->first);
544 stmt->setUInt64(1, GetOwner()->GetGUID().GetCounter());
545 trans->Append(stmt);
546
547 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_CHAR_ACHIEVEMENT);
548 stmt->setUInt64(0, GetOwner()->GetGUID().GetCounter());
549 stmt->setUInt16(1, iter->first);
550 stmt->setUInt32(2, uint32(iter->second.date));
551 trans->Append(stmt);
552
553 iter->second.changed = false;
554 }
555 }
556
557 if (!m_criteriaProgress.empty())
558 {
559 for (CriteriaProgressMap::iterator iter = m_criteriaProgress.begin(); iter != m_criteriaProgress.end(); ++iter)
560 {
561 if (!iter->second.changed)
562 continue;
563
564 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_CHAR_ACHIEVEMENT_PROGRESS_BY_CRITERIA);
565 stmt->setUInt64(0, GetOwner()->GetGUID().GetCounter());
566 stmt->setUInt32(1, iter->first);
567 trans->Append(stmt);
568
569 if (iter->second.counter)
570 {
571 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_CHAR_ACHIEVEMENT_PROGRESS);
572 stmt->setUInt64(0, GetOwner()->GetGUID().GetCounter());
573 stmt->setUInt32(1, iter->first);
574 stmt->setUInt32(2, iter->second.counter);
575 stmt->setUInt32(3, uint32(iter->second.date));
576 trans->Append(stmt);
577 }
578
579 iter->second.changed = false;
580 }
581 }
582}

584template<>
585void AchievementMgr<Guild>::SaveToDB(SQLTransaction& trans)
586{
587 PreparedStatement* stmt;
588 std::ostringstream guidstr;
589 for (CompletedAchievementMap::const_iterator itr = m_completedAchievements.begin(); itr != m_completedAchievements.end(); ++itr)
590 {
591 if (!itr->second.changed)
592 continue;
593
594 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_GUILD_ACHIEVEMENT);
595 stmt->setUInt64(0, GetOwner()->GetId());
596 stmt->setUInt16(1, itr->first);
597 trans->Append(stmt);
598
599 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_GUILD_ACHIEVEMENT);
600 stmt->setUInt64(0, GetOwner()->GetId());
601 stmt->setUInt16(1, itr->first);
602 stmt->setUInt32(2, itr->second.date);
603 for (GuidSet::const_iterator gItr = itr->second.guids.begin(); gItr != itr->second.guids.end(); ++gItr)
604 guidstr << gItr->GetCounter() << ',';
605
606 stmt->setString(3, guidstr.str());
607 trans->Append(stmt);
608
609 guidstr.str("");
610 }
611
612 for (CriteriaProgressMap::const_iterator itr = m_criteriaProgress.begin(); itr != m_criteriaProgress.end(); ++itr)
613 {
614 if (!itr->second.changed)
615 continue;
616
617 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_GUILD_ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA);
618 stmt->setUInt64(0, GetOwner()->GetId());
619 stmt->setUInt32(1, itr->first);
620 trans->Append(stmt);
621
622 stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_INS_GUILD_ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA);
623 stmt->setUInt64(0, GetOwner()->GetId());
624 stmt->setUInt32(1, itr->first);
625 stmt->setUInt64(2, itr->second.counter);
626 stmt->setUInt32(3, itr->second.date);
627 stmt->setUInt64(4, itr->second.PlayerGUID.GetCounter());
628 trans->Append(stmt);

631template<class T>
632void AchievementMgr<T>::LoadFromDB(PreparedQueryResult /*achievementResult*/, PreparedQueryResult /*criteriaResult*/)
633{
634}
635
636template<>
637void AchievementMgr<Player>::LoadFromDB(PreparedQueryResult achievementResult, PreparedQueryResult criteriaResult)
638{
639 if (achievementResult)
640 {
641 do
642 {
643 Field* fields = achievementResult->Fetch();
644 uint32 achievementid = fields[0].GetUInt16();
645
646 // must not happen: cleanup at server startup in sAchievementMgr->LoadCompletedAchievements()
647 AchievementEntry const* achievement = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievement(achievementid);
648 if (!achievement)
649 continue;
650
651 CompletedAchievementData& ca = m_completedAchievements[achievementid];
652 ca.date = time_t(fields[1].GetUInt32());
653 ca.changed = false;
654
655 _achievementPoints += achievement->Points;
656
657 // title achievement rewards are retroactive
658 if (AchievementReward const* reward = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementReward(achievement))
659 if (uint32 titleId = reward->titleId[Player::TeamForRace(GetOwner()->getRace()) == ALLIANCE ? 0 : 1])
660 if (CharTitlesEntry const* titleEntry = sCharTitlesStore.LookupEntry(titleId))
661 GetOwner()->SetTitle(titleEntry);
662
663 }
664 while (achievementResult->NextRow());
665 }
666
667 if (criteriaResult)
668 {
669 time_t now = time(NULL);
670 do
671 {
672 Field* fields = criteriaResult->Fetch();
673 uint32 id = fields[0].GetUInt32();
674 uint64 counter = fields[1].GetUInt64();
675 time_t date = time_t(fields[2].GetUInt32());
676
677 AchievementCriteria const* criteria = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteria(id);
678 if (!criteria)
679 {
680 // we will remove not existed criteria for all characters
681 TC_LOG_ERROR("achievement", "Non-existing achievement criteria %u data removed from table `character_achievement_progress`.", id);
682
683 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_INVALID_ACHIEV_PROGRESS_CRITERIA);
684 stmt->setUInt32(0, uint16(id));
685 CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
686
687 continue;
688 }
689
690 if (criteria->Entry->StartTimer && time_t(date + criteria->Entry->StartTimer) < now)
691 continue;
692
693 CriteriaProgress& progress = m_criteriaProgress[id];
694 progress.counter = counter;
695 progress.date = date;
696 progress.changed = false;
697 }
698 while (criteriaResult->NextRow());
699 }
700}
701
702template<>
703void AchievementMgr<Guild>::LoadFromDB(PreparedQueryResult achievementResult, PreparedQueryResult criteriaResult)
704{
705 if (achievementResult)
706 {
707 do
708 {
709 Field* fields = achievementResult->Fetch();
710 uint32 achievementid = fields[0].GetUInt16();
711
712 // must not happen: cleanup at server startup in sAchievementMgr->LoadCompletedAchievements()
713 AchievementEntry const* achievement = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievement(achievementid);
714 if (!achievement)
715 continue;
716
717 CompletedAchievementData& ca = m_completedAchievements[achievementid];
718 ca.date = time_t(fields[1].GetUInt32());
719 Tokenizer guids(fields[2].GetString(), ' ');
720 for (uint32 i = 0; i < guids.size(); ++i)
721 ca.guids.insert(ObjectGuid::Create<HighGuid::Player>(uint64(strtoull(guids[i], nullptr, 10))));
722
723 ca.changed = false;
724
725 _achievementPoints += achievement->Points;
726 }
727 while (achievementResult->NextRow());
728 }
729
730 if (criteriaResult)
731 {
732 time_t now = time(NULL);
733 do
734 {
735 Field* fields = criteriaResult->Fetch();
736 uint32 id = fields[0].GetUInt32();
737 uint64 counter = fields[1].GetUInt64();
738 time_t date = time_t(fields[2].GetUInt32());
739 ObjectGuid::LowType guid = fields[3].GetUInt64();
740
741 AchievementCriteria const* criteria = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteria(id);
742 if (!criteria)
743 {
744 // we will remove not existed criteria for all guilds
745 TC_LOG_ERROR("achievement", "Non-existing achievement criteria %u data removed from table `guild_achievement_progress`.", id);
746
747 PreparedStatement* stmt = CharacterDatabase.GetPreparedStatement(CHAR_DEL_INVALID_ACHIEV_PROGRESS_CRITERIA_GUILD);
748 stmt->setUInt32(0, uint16(id));
749 CharacterDatabase.Execute(stmt);
750 continue;
751 }
752
753 if (criteria->Entry->StartTimer && time_t(date + criteria->Entry->StartTimer) < now)
754 continue;
755
756 CriteriaProgress& progress = m_criteriaProgress[id];
757 progress.counter = counter;
758 progress.date = date;
759 progress.PlayerGUID = ObjectGuid::Create<HighGuid::Player>(guid);
760 progress.changed = false;
761 } while (criteriaResult->NextRow());
762 }
763}

765template<class T>
766void AchievementMgr<T>::Reset()
767{
768}
769
770template<>
771void AchievementMgr<Player>::Reset()
772{
773 for (CompletedAchievementMap::const_iterator iter = m_completedAchievements.begin(); iter != m_completedAchievements.end(); ++iter)
774 {
775 WorldPackets::Achievement::AchievementDeleted achievementDeleted;
776 achievementDeleted.AchievementID = iter->first;
777 SendPacket(achievementDeleted.Write());
778 }
779
780 for (CriteriaProgressMap::const_iterator iter = m_criteriaProgress.begin(); iter != m_criteriaProgress.end(); ++iter)
781 {
782 WorldPackets::Achievement::CriteriaDeleted criteriaDeleted;
783 criteriaDeleted.CriteriaID = iter->first;
784 SendPacket(criteriaDeleted.Write());
785 }
786
787 m_completedAchievements.clear();
788 _achievementPoints = 0;
789 m_criteriaProgress.clear();
790 DeleteFromDB(GetOwner()->GetGUID());
791
792 // re-fill data
793 CheckAllAchievementCriteria(GetOwner());
794}
795
796template<>
797void AchievementMgr<Guild>::Reset()
798{
799 ObjectGuid guid = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
800 for (CompletedAchievementMap::const_iterator iter = m_completedAchievements.begin(); iter != m_completedAchievements.end(); ++iter)
801 {
802 WorldPackets::Achievement::GuildAchievementDeleted guildAchievementDeleted;
803 guildAchievementDeleted.AchievementID = iter->first;
804 guildAchievementDeleted.GuildGUID = guid;
805 guildAchievementDeleted.TimeDeleted = time(NULL);
806 SendPacket(guildAchievementDeleted.Write());
807 }
808
809 while (!m_criteriaProgress.empty())
810 if (AchievementCriteria const* criteria = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteria(m_criteriaProgress.begin()->first))
811 RemoveCriteriaProgress(criteria);
812
813 _achievementPoints = 0;
814 m_completedAchievements.clear();
815 DeleteFromDB(GetOwner()->GetGUID());
816}

818template<class T>
819void AchievementMgr<T>::SendAchievementEarned(AchievementEntry const* achievement) const
820{
821 // Don't send for achievements with ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_HIDDEN
822 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_HIDDEN)
823 return;
824
825 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "AchievementMgr::SendAchievementEarned(%u)", achievement->ID);
826
827 if (Guild* guild = sGuildMgr->GetGuildById(GetOwner()->GetGuildId()))
828 {
829 Trinity::BroadcastTextBuilder _builder(GetOwner(), CHAT_MSG_GUILD_ACHIEVEMENT, BROADCAST_TEXT_ACHIEVEMENT_EARNED, GetOwner(), achievement->ID);
830 Trinity::LocalizedPacketDo<Trinity::BroadcastTextBuilder> _localizer(_builder);
831 guild->BroadcastWorker(_localizer, GetOwner());
832 }
833
834 if (achievement->Flags & (ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_REALM_FIRST_KILL | ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_REALM_FIRST_REACH))
835 {
836 // broadcast realm first reached
837 WorldPackets::Achievement::ServerFirstAchievement serverFirstAchievement;
838 serverFirstAchievement.Name = GetOwner()->GetName();
839 serverFirstAchievement.PlayerGUID = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
840 serverFirstAchievement.AchievementID = achievement->ID;
841 sWorld->SendGlobalMessage(serverFirstAchievement.Write());
842 }
843 // if player is in world he can tell his friends about new achievement
844 else if (GetOwner()->IsInWorld())
845 {
846 Trinity::BroadcastTextBuilder _builder(GetOwner(), CHAT_MSG_ACHIEVEMENT, BROADCAST_TEXT_ACHIEVEMENT_EARNED, GetOwner(), achievement->ID);
847 Trinity::LocalizedPacketDo<Trinity::BroadcastTextBuilder> _localizer(_builder);
848 Trinity::PlayerDistWorker<Trinity::LocalizedPacketDo<Trinity::BroadcastTextBuilder> > _worker(GetOwner(), sWorld->getFloatConfig(CONFIG_LISTEN_RANGE_SAY), _localizer);
849 GetOwner()->VisitNearbyWorldObject(sWorld->getFloatConfig(CONFIG_LISTEN_RANGE_SAY), _worker);
850 }
851
852 WorldPackets::Achievement::AchievementEarned achievementEarned;
853 achievementEarned.Sender = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
854 achievementEarned.Earner = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
855 achievementEarned.EarnerNativeRealm = achievementEarned.EarnerVirtualRealm = GetVirtualRealmAddress();
856 achievementEarned.AchievementID = achievement->ID;
857 achievementEarned.Time = time(NULL);
858 GetOwner()->SendMessageToSetInRange(achievementEarned.Write(), sWorld->getFloatConfig(CONFIG_LISTEN_RANGE_SAY), true);
859}
860
861template<>
862void AchievementMgr<Guild>::SendAchievementEarned(AchievementEntry const* achievement) const
863{
864 if (achievement->Flags & (ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_REALM_FIRST_KILL | ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_REALM_FIRST_REACH))
865 {
866 // broadcast realm first reached
867 WorldPackets::Achievement::ServerFirstAchievement serverFirstAchievement;
868 serverFirstAchievement.Name = GetOwner()->GetName();
869 serverFirstAchievement.PlayerGUID = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
870 serverFirstAchievement.AchievementID = achievement->ID;
871 serverFirstAchievement.GuildAchievement = true;
872 sWorld->SendGlobalMessage(serverFirstAchievement.Write());
873 }
874
875 WorldPackets::Achievement::GuildAchievementEarned guildAchievementEarned;
876 guildAchievementEarned.AchievementID = achievement->ID;
877 guildAchievementEarned.GuildGUID = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
878 guildAchievementEarned.TimeEarned = time(NULL);
879 SendPacket(guildAchievementEarned.Write());
880}

882template<class T>

884{
885}
886
887template<>
888void AchievementMgr<Player>::SendCriteriaUpdate(AchievementCriteria const* criteria, CriteriaProgress const* progress, uint32 timeElapsed, bool timedCompleted) const
889{
890 WorldPackets::Achievement::CriteriaUpdate criteriaUpdate;
891
892 criteriaUpdate.CriteriaID = criteria->ID;
893 criteriaUpdate.Quantity = progress->counter;
894 criteriaUpdate.PlayerGUID = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
895 if (criteria->Entry->StartTimer)
896 criteriaUpdate.Flags = timedCompleted ? 1 : 0; // 1 is for keeping the counter at 0 in client
897
898 criteriaUpdate.Flags = 0;
899 criteriaUpdate.CurrentTime = progress->date;
900 criteriaUpdate.ElapsedTime = timeElapsed;
901 criteriaUpdate.CreationTime = 0;
902
903 SendPacket(criteriaUpdate.Write());
904}

906template<>
907void AchievementMgr<Guild>::SendCriteriaUpdate(AchievementCriteria const* entry, CriteriaProgress const* progress, uint32 /*timeElapsed*/, bool /*timedCompleted*/) const
908{
909 WorldPackets::Achievement::GuildCriteriaUpdate guildCriteriaUpdate;
910 guildCriteriaUpdate.Progress.resize(1);
911
912 WorldPackets::Achievement::GuildCriteriaProgress& guildCriteriaProgress = guildCriteriaUpdate.Progress[0];
913 guildCriteriaProgress.CriteriaID = entry->ID;
914 guildCriteriaProgress.DateCreated = 0;
915 guildCriteriaProgress.DateStarted = 0;
916 guildCriteriaProgress.DateUpdated = progress->date;
917 guildCriteriaProgress.Quantity = progress->counter;
918 guildCriteriaProgress.PlayerGUID = progress->PlayerGUID;
919 guildCriteriaProgress.Flags = 0;
920
921 GetOwner()->BroadcastPacketIfTrackingAchievement(guildCriteriaUpdate.Write(), entry->ID);
922}

924template<class T>
925void AchievementMgr<T>::SendAllTrackedCriterias(Player* /*receiver*/, std::set<uint32> const& /*trackedCriterias*/) const
926{
927}
928
929template<>
930void AchievementMgr<Guild>::SendAllTrackedCriterias(Player* receiver, std::set<uint32> const& trackedCriterias) const
931{
932 WorldPackets::Achievement::GuildCriteriaUpdate guildCriteriaUpdate;
933 guildCriteriaUpdate.Progress.reserve(trackedCriterias.size());
934
935 for (uint32 criteriaId : trackedCriterias)
936 {
937 auto progress = m_criteriaProgress.find(criteriaId);
938 if (progress == m_criteriaProgress.end())
939 continue;
940
941 WorldPackets::Achievement::GuildCriteriaProgress guildCriteriaProgress;
942 guildCriteriaProgress.CriteriaID = criteriaId;
943 guildCriteriaProgress.DateCreated = 0;
944 guildCriteriaProgress.DateStarted = 0;
945 guildCriteriaProgress.DateUpdated = progress->second.date;
946 guildCriteriaProgress.Quantity = progress->second.counter;
947 guildCriteriaProgress.PlayerGUID = progress->second.PlayerGUID;
948 guildCriteriaProgress.Flags = 0;
949
950 guildCriteriaUpdate.Progress.push_back(guildCriteriaProgress);
951 }
952
953 receiver->GetSession()->SendPacket(guildCriteriaUpdate.Write());
954}

956/**
957 * called at player login. The player might have fulfilled some achievements when the achievement system wasn't working yet
958 */
959template<class T>
960void AchievementMgr<T>::CheckAllAchievementCriteria(Player* referencePlayer)
961{
962 // suppress sending packets
963 for (uint32 i = 0; i < ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_TOTAL; ++i)
964 UpdateAchievementCriteria(AchievementCriteriaTypes(i), 0, 0, 0, NULL, referencePlayer);
965}

967// Helper function to avoid having to specialize template for a 800 line long function
968template <typename T> static bool IsGuild() { return false; }
969template<> bool IsGuild<Guild>() { return true; }
970
971/**
972 * this function will be called whenever the user might have done a criteria relevant action
973 */
974template<class T>
975void AchievementMgr<T>::UpdateAchievementCriteria(AchievementCriteriaTypes type, uint64 miscValue1 /*= 0*/, uint64 miscValue2 /*= 0*/, uint64 miscValue3 /*= 0*/, Unit const* unit /*= NULL*/, Player* referencePlayer /*= NULL*/)
976{
977 if (type >= ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_TOTAL)
978 {
979 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "UpdateAchievementCriteria: Wrong criteria type %u", type);
980 return;
981 }
982
983 if (!referencePlayer)
984 {
985 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "UpdateAchievementCriteria: Player is NULL! Cant update criteria");
986 return;
987 }
988
989 // disable for gamemasters with GM-mode enabled
990 if (referencePlayer->IsGameMaster())
991 {
992 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "UpdateAchievementCriteria: [Player %s GM mode on] %s, %s (%u), " UI64FMTD ", " UI64FMTD ", " UI64FMTD
993 , referencePlayer->GetName().c_str(), GetOwner()->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(type), type, miscValue1, miscValue2, miscValue3);
994 return;
995 }
996
997 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "UpdateAchievementCriteria: %s, %s (%u), " UI64FMTD ", " UI64FMTD ", " UI64FMTD
998 , GetOwner()->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(type), type, miscValue1, miscValue2, miscValue3);
999
1000 // Lua_GetGuildLevelEnabled() is checked in achievement UI to display guild tab
1001 //if (IsGuild<T>() && !sWorld->getBoolConfig(CONFIG_GUILD_LEVELING_ENABLED))
1002 // return;
1003
1004 AchievementCriteriaList const& achievementCriteriaList = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaByType(type, IsGuild<T>());
1005 for (AchievementCriteria const* achievementCriteria : achievementCriteriaList)
1006 {
1007 AchievementCriteriaTreeList const* trees = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaTreesByCriteria(achievementCriteria->ID);
1008
1009 if (!CanUpdateCriteria(achievementCriteria, trees, miscValue1, miscValue2, miscValue3, unit, referencePlayer))
1010 continue;
1011
1012 // requirements not found in the dbc
1013 if (AchievementCriteriaDataSet const* data = sAchievementMgr->GetCriteriaDataSet(achievementCriteria))
1014 if (!data->Meets(referencePlayer, unit, miscValue1))
1015 continue;
1016
1017 switch (type)
1018 {
1019 // std. case: increment at 1
1020 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_NUMBER_OF_TALENT_RESETS:
1021 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LOSE_DUEL:
1022 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CREATE_AUCTION:
1023 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WON_AUCTIONS: /* FIXME: for online player only currently */
1024 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_NEED:
1025 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_GREED:
1026 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_QUEST_ABANDONED:
1027 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_FLIGHT_PATHS_TAKEN:
1028 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ACCEPTED_SUMMONINGS:
1029 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LOOT_EPIC_ITEM:
1030 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_RECEIVE_EPIC_ITEM:
1031 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATH:
1032 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_DAILY_QUEST:
1033 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATH_AT_MAP:
1034 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATH_IN_DUNGEON:
1035 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KILLED_BY_CREATURE:
1036 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KILLED_BY_PLAYER:
1037 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATHS_FROM:
1038 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BE_SPELL_TARGET:
1039 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BE_SPELL_TARGET2:
1040 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CAST_SPELL:
1041 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CAST_SPELL2:
1042 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_RATED_ARENA:
1043 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_USE_ITEM:
1044 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_NEED_ON_LOOT:
1045 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_GREED_ON_LOOT:
1046 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DO_EMOTE:
1047 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_USE_GAMEOBJECT:
1048 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_FISH_IN_GAMEOBJECT:
1049 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_DUEL:
1050 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HK_CLASS:
1051 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HK_RACE:
1052 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BG_OBJECTIVE_CAPTURE:
1053 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HONORABLE_KILL:
1054 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_SPECIAL_PVP_KILL:
1055 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_GET_KILLING_BLOWS:
1056 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HONORABLE_KILL_AT_AREA:
1057 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_ARENA: // This also behaves like ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_RATED_ARENA
1058 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ON_LOGIN:
1059 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_PLACE_GARRISON_BUILDING:
1060 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_OWN_BATTLE_PET_COUNT:
1061 SetCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria, 1, referencePlayer, PROGRESS_ACCUMULATE);
1062 break;
1063 // std case: increment at miscValue1
1064 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_MONEY_FROM_VENDORS:
1065 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_GOLD_SPENT_FOR_TALENTS:
1066 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_MONEY_FROM_QUEST_REWARD:

1112 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_DAILY_QUEST_DAILY:
1113 {
1114 time_t nextDailyResetTime = sWorld->GetNextDailyQuestsResetTime();
1115 CriteriaProgress *progress = GetCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria);
1116
1117 if (!miscValue1) // Login case.
1118 {
1119 // reset if player missed one day.
1120 if (progress && progress->date < (nextDailyResetTime - 2 * DAY))
1121 SetCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria, 0, referencePlayer, PROGRESS_SET);
1122 continue;
1123 }
1124
1125 ProgressType progressType;
1126 if (!progress)
1127 // 1st time. Start count.
1128 progressType = PROGRESS_SET;
1129 else if (progress->date < (nextDailyResetTime - 2 * DAY))
1130 // last progress is older than 2 days. Player missed 1 day => Restart count.
1131 progressType = PROGRESS_SET;
1132 else if (progress->date < (nextDailyResetTime - DAY))
1133 // last progress is between 1 and 2 days. => 1st time of the day.
1134 progressType = PROGRESS_ACCUMULATE;
1135 else
1136 // last progress is within the day before the reset => Already counted today.
1137 continue;

1189 spellIter != referencePlayer->GetSpellMap().end();
1190 ++spellIter)
1191 {
1192 SkillLineAbilityMapBounds bounds = sSpellMgr->GetSkillLineAbilityMapBounds(spellIter->first);
1193 for (SkillLineAbilityMap::const_iterator skillIter = bounds.first; skillIter != bounds.second; ++skillIter)
1194 {
1195 if (skillIter->second->SkillLine == achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.SkillID)

1200 break;
1201 }

1210 break;

1213 break;
1214 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HIGHEST_GOLD_VALUE_OWNED:
1215 SetCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria, referencePlayer->GetMoney(), referencePlayer, PROGRESS_HIGHEST);
1216 break;
1217 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EARN_ACHIEVEMENT_POINTS:
1218 if (!miscValue1)
1219 SetCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria, _achievementPoints, referencePlayer, PROGRESS_SET);
1220 else
1221 SetCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria, miscValue1, referencePlayer, PROGRESS_ACCUMULATE);
1222 break;
1223 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HIGHEST_PERSONAL_RATING:
1224 {
1225 uint32 reqTeamType = achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.TeamType;
1226
1227 if (miscValue1)
1228 {
1229 if (miscValue2 != reqTeamType)
1230 continue;
1231
1232 SetCriteriaProgress(achievementCriteria, miscValue1, referencePlayer, PROGRESS_HIGHEST);
1233 }
1234 else // login case
1235 {
1236 for (uint32 arena_slot = 0; arena_slot < MAX_ARENA_SLOT; ++arena_slot)

1300 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LEARN_GARRISON_BLUEPRINT_COUNT:
1301 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_GARRISON_SHIPMENT:
1302 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_RAISE_GARRISON_FOLLOWER_ITEM_LEVEL:

1306 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_OWN_HEIRLOOMS:
1307 break; // Not implemented yet :(
1308 }
1309
1310 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : *trees)
1311 {
1312 if (IsCompletedCriteriaTree(tree))
1313 CompletedCriteriaFor(tree->Achievement, referencePlayer);
1314
1315 // check again the completeness for SUMM and REQ COUNT achievements,
1316 // as they don't depend on the completed criteria but on the sum of the progress of each individual criteria
1317 if (tree->Achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_SUMM)
1318 if (IsCompletedAchievement(tree->Achievement))
1319 CompletedAchievement(tree->Achievement, referencePlayer);
1320
1321 if (AchievementEntryList const* achRefList = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementByReferencedId(tree->Achievement->ID))
1322 for (AchievementEntry const* refAchievement : *achRefList)
1323 if (IsCompletedAchievement(refAchievement))
1324 CompletedAchievement(refAchievement, referencePlayer);
1325 }
1326 }
1327}

1329// Only player personal achievements require instance id to check realm firsts
1330// Guild restrictions are handled with additionalConditionType/additionalConditionValue
1331template<class T>
1332static uint32 GetInstanceId(T* /*object*/) { return 0xFFFFFFFF; }
1333
1334template<>
1335uint32 GetInstanceId(Player* player) { return player->GetInstanceId(); }
1336
1337template<class T>
1338bool AchievementMgr<T>::IsCompletedCriteriaTree(AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree)
1339{
1340 AchievementEntry const* achievement = tree->Achievement;
1341 if (!achievement)
1342 return false;
1343
1344 // counter can never complete
1345 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_COUNTER)
1346 return false;
1347
1348 if (achievement->Flags & (ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_REALM_FIRST_REACH | ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_REALM_FIRST_KILL))
1349 {
1350 // someone on this realm has already completed that achievement
1351 if (sAchievementMgr->IsRealmCompleted(achievement, GetInstanceId(GetOwner())))
1352 return false;
1353 }
1354
1355 uint64 requiredCount = tree->Entry->Amount;
1356 uint64 completedCount = 0;
1357 uint32 op = tree->Entry->Operator;
1358 bool hasAll = true;
1359
1360 // Check criteria we depend on first
1361 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* node : tree->Children)
1362 {
1363 if (IsCompletedCriteriaTree(node))
1364 ++completedCount;
1365 else
1366 hasAll = false;
1367
1368 if (op & ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TREE_OPERATOR_ANY && completedCount >= requiredCount)
1369 {
1370 if (!tree->Criteria)
1371 return true;
1372
1373 break;
1374 }
1375 }
1376
1377 if (op & ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TREE_OPERATOR_ANY && completedCount < requiredCount)
1378 return false;
1379
1380 if (op & ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TREE_OPERATOR_ALL && !hasAll)
1381 return false;
1382
1383 if (!tree->Criteria)
1384 return true;
1385
1386 return IsCompletedCriteria(tree->Criteria, requiredCount);
1387}

1493 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_QUEST_ABANDONED:
1494 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_FLIGHT_PATHS_TAKEN:
1495 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ACCEPTED_SUMMONINGS:
1496 default:
1497 break;
1498 }
1499
1500 return false;
1501}
1502
1503template<class T>
1504void AchievementMgr<T>::CompletedCriteriaFor(AchievementEntry const* achievement, Player* referencePlayer)
1505{
1506 // counter can never complete
1507 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_COUNTER)
1508 return;
1509
1510 // already completed and stored
1511 if (HasAchieved(achievement->ID))
1512 return;
1513
1514 if (IsCompletedAchievement(achievement))
1515 CompletedAchievement(achievement, referencePlayer);
1516}
1517
1518template<class T>
1519bool AchievementMgr<T>::IsCompletedAchievement(AchievementEntry const* entry)
1520{
1521 // counter can never complete
1522 if (entry->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_COUNTER)
1523 return false;
1524
1525 AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaTree(entry->CriteriaTree);
1526 if (!tree)
1527 return false;
1528
1529 // For SUMM achievements, we have to count the progress of each criteria of the achievement.
1530 // Oddly, the target count is NOT contained in the achievement, but in each individual criteria
1531 if (entry->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_SUMM)
1532 {
1533 uint64 progress = 0;
1534 sAchievementMgr->WalkCriteriaTree(tree, [this, &progress](AchievementCriteriaTree const* criteriaTree)
1535 {
1536 if (criteriaTree->Criteria)
1537 if (CriteriaProgress const* criteriaProgress = this->GetCriteriaProgress(criteriaTree->Criteria))
1538 progress += criteriaProgress->counter;
1539 });
1540 return progress >= tree->Entry->Amount;
1541 }
1542
1543 return IsCompletedCriteriaTree(tree);
1544}
1545
1546template<class T>
1547CriteriaProgress* AchievementMgr<T>::GetCriteriaProgress(AchievementCriteria const* entry)
1548{
1549 CriteriaProgressMap::iterator iter = m_criteriaProgress.find(entry->ID);
1550
1551 if (iter == m_criteriaProgress.end())
1552 return NULL;
1553
1554 return &(iter->second);
1555}
1556
1557template<class T>
1558void AchievementMgr<T>::SetCriteriaProgress(AchievementCriteria const* criteria, uint64 changeValue, Player* referencePlayer, ProgressType ptype)
1559{
1560 // Don't allow to cheat - doing timed achievements without timer active
1561 AchievementCriteriaTreeList const* trees = nullptr;
1562 if (criteria->Entry->StartTimer)
1563 {
1564 trees = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaTreesByCriteria(criteria->ID);
1565 if (!trees)
1566 return;
1567
1568 bool hasTreeForTimed = false;
1569 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : *trees)
1570 {
1571 auto timedIter = m_timedAchievements.find(tree->ID);
1572 if (timedIter != m_timedAchievements.end())
1573 {
1574 hasTreeForTimed = true;
1575 break;
1576 }
1577
1578 }
1579
1580 if (!hasTreeForTimed)
1581 return;
1582 }
1583
1584 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "SetCriteriaProgress(%u, " UI64FMTD ") for (%s)",
1585 criteria->ID, changeValue, GetOwner()->GetGUID().ToString().c_str());
1586
1587 CriteriaProgress* progress = GetCriteriaProgress(criteria);
1588 if (!progress)
1589 {
1590 // not create record for 0 counter but allow it for timed achievements
1591 // we will need to send 0 progress to client to start the timer
1592 if (changeValue == 0 && !criteria->Entry->StartTimer)
1593 return;
1594
1595 progress = &m_criteriaProgress[criteria->ID];
1596 progress->counter = changeValue;
1597 }
1598 else
1599 {
1600 uint64 newValue = 0;
1601 switch (ptype)
1602 {
1603 case PROGRESS_SET:
1604 newValue = changeValue;
1605 break;
1606 case PROGRESS_ACCUMULATE:
1607 {
1608 // avoid overflow
1609 uint64 max_value = std::numeric_limits<uint64>::max();
1610 newValue = max_value - progress->counter > changeValue ? progress->counter + changeValue : max_value;
1611 break;
1612 }
1613 case PROGRESS_HIGHEST:
1614 newValue = progress->counter < changeValue ? changeValue : progress->counter;
1615 break;
1616 }
1617
1618 // not update (not mark as changed) if counter will have same value
1619 if (progress->counter == newValue && !criteria->Entry->StartTimer)
1620 return;
1621
1622 progress->counter = newValue;
1623 }
1624
1625 progress->changed = true;
1626 progress->date = time(NULL); // set the date to the latest update.
1627 progress->PlayerGUID = referencePlayer->GetGUID();
1628
1629 uint32 timeElapsed = 0;
1630
1631 if (criteria->Entry->StartTimer)
1632 {
1633 ASSERT(trees);
1634
1635 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : *trees)
1636 {
1637 auto timedIter = m_timedAchievements.find(tree->ID);
1638 if (timedIter != m_timedAchievements.end())
1639 {
1640 // Client expects this in packet
1641 timeElapsed = criteria->Entry->StartTimer - (timedIter->second / IN_MILLISECONDS);
1642
1643 // Remove the timer, we wont need it anymore
1644 if (IsCompletedCriteriaTree(tree))
1645 m_timedAchievements.erase(timedIter);
1646 }
1647 }
1648 }
1649
1650 SendCriteriaUpdate(criteria, progress, timeElapsed, true);
1651}
1652
1653template<class T>
1654void AchievementMgr<T>::UpdateTimedAchievements(uint32 timeDiff)
1655{
1656 if (!m_timedAchievements.empty())
1657 {
1658 for (TimedAchievementMap::iterator itr = m_timedAchievements.begin(); itr != m_timedAchievements.end();)
1659 {
1660 // Time is up, remove timer and reset progress
1661 if (itr->second <= timeDiff)
1662 {
1663 AchievementCriteriaTree const* criteriaTree = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaTree(itr->first);
1664 if (criteriaTree->Criteria)
1665 RemoveCriteriaProgress(criteriaTree->Criteria);
1666
1667 m_timedAchievements.erase(itr++);
1668 }
1669 else
1670 {
1671 itr->second -= timeDiff;
1672 ++itr;
1673 }
1674 }
1675 }
1676}
1677
1678template<class T>
1679void AchievementMgr<T>::StartTimedAchievement(AchievementCriteriaTimedTypes /*type*/, uint32 /*entry*/, uint32 /*timeLost = 0*/)
1680{
1681}
1682
1683template<>
1684void AchievementMgr<Player>::StartTimedAchievement(AchievementCriteriaTimedTypes type, uint32 entry, uint32 timeLost /* = 0 */)
1685{
1686 AchievementCriteriaList const& achievementCriteriaList = sAchievementMgr->GetTimedAchievementCriteriaByType(type);
1687 for (AchievementCriteria const* criteria : achievementCriteriaList)
1688 {
1689 if (criteria->Entry->StartAsset != entry)
1690 continue;
1691
1692 AchievementCriteriaTreeList const* trees = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaTreesByCriteria(criteria->ID);
1693 bool canStart = false;
1694 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : *trees)
1695 {
1696 if (m_timedAchievements.find(tree->ID) == m_timedAchievements.end() && !IsCompletedCriteriaTree(tree))
1697 {
1698 // Start the timer
1699 if (criteria->Entry->StartTimer * IN_MILLISECONDS > timeLost)
1700 {
1701 m_timedAchievements[tree->ID] = criteria->Entry->StartTimer * IN_MILLISECONDS - timeLost;
1702 canStart = true;
1703 }
1704 }
1705 }
1706
1707 if (!canStart)
1708 continue;
1709
1710 // and at client too
1711 SetCriteriaProgress(criteria, 0, GetOwner(), PROGRESS_SET);
1712 }
1713}
1714
1715template<class T>
1716void AchievementMgr<T>::RemoveTimedAchievement(AchievementCriteriaTimedTypes type, uint32 entry)
1717{
1718 AchievementCriteriaList const& achievementCriteriaList = sAchievementMgr->GetTimedAchievementCriteriaByType(type);
1719 for (AchievementCriteria const* criteria : achievementCriteriaList)
1720 {
1721 if (criteria->Entry->StartAsset != entry)
1722 continue;
1723
1724 AchievementCriteriaTreeList const* trees = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementCriteriaTreesByCriteria(criteria->ID);
1725 // Remove the timer from all trees
1726 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : *trees)
1727 m_timedAchievements.erase(tree->ID);
1728
1729 // remove progress
1730 RemoveCriteriaProgress(criteria);
1731 }
1732}
1733
1734template<>
1735void AchievementMgr<Player>::CompletedAchievement(AchievementEntry const* achievement, Player* referencePlayer)
1736{
1737 // disable for gamemasters with GM-mode enabled
1738 if (GetOwner()->IsGameMaster())
1739 return;
1740
1741 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_COUNTER || HasAchieved(achievement->ID))
1742 return;
1743
1744 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_SHOW_IN_GUILD_NEWS)
1745 if (Guild* guild = referencePlayer->GetGuild())
1746 guild->AddGuildNews(GUILD_NEWS_PLAYER_ACHIEVEMENT, referencePlayer->GetGUID(), achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_SHOW_IN_GUILD_HEADER, achievement->ID);
1747
1748 if (!GetOwner()->GetSession()->PlayerLoading())
1749 SendAchievementEarned(achievement);
1750
1751 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "AchievementMgr::CompletedAchievement(%u). %s %s",
1752 achievement->ID, GetOwner()->GetGUID().ToString().c_str(), GetOwner()->GetName().c_str());
1753
1754 CompletedAchievementData& ca = m_completedAchievements[achievement->ID];
1755 ca.date = time(NULL);
1756 ca.changed = true;
1757
1758 sAchievementMgr->SetRealmCompleted(achievement, GetOwner()->GetInstanceId());
1759
1760 _achievementPoints += achievement->Points;
1761
1762 UpdateAchievementCriteria(ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_ACHIEVEMENT, 0, 0, 0, NULL, referencePlayer);
1763 UpdateAchievementCriteria(ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EARN_ACHIEVEMENT_POINTS, achievement->Points, 0, 0, NULL, referencePlayer);
1764
1765 // reward items and titles if any
1766 AchievementReward const* reward = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementReward(achievement);
1767
1768 // no rewards
1769 if (!reward)
1770 return;
1771
1772 // titles
1773 //! Currently there's only one achievement that deals with gender-specific titles.
1774 //! Since no common attributes were found, (not even in titleRewardFlags field)
1775 //! we explicitly check by ID. Maybe in the future we could move the achievement_reward
1776 //! condition fields to the condition system.
1777 if (uint32 titleId = reward->titleId[achievement->ID == 1793 ? GetOwner()->GetByteValue(PLAYER_BYTES_3, PLAYER_BYTES_3_OFFSET_GENDER) : (GetOwner()->GetTeam() == ALLIANCE ? 0 : 1)])
1778 if (CharTitlesEntry const* titleEntry = sCharTitlesStore.LookupEntry(titleId))
1779 GetOwner()->SetTitle(titleEntry);
1780
1781 // mail
1782 if (reward->sender)
1783 {
1784 MailDraft draft(reward->mailTemplate);
1785
1786 if (!reward->mailTemplate)
1787 {
1788 // subject and text
1789 std::string subject = reward->subject;
1790 std::string text = reward->text;
1791
1792 LocaleConstant localeConstant = GetOwner()->GetSession()->GetSessionDbLocaleIndex();
1793 if (localeConstant >= LOCALE_enUS)
1794 {
1795 if (AchievementRewardLocale const* loc = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievementRewardLocale(achievement))
1796 {
1797 ObjectMgr::GetLocaleString(loc->subject, localeConstant, subject);
1798 ObjectMgr::GetLocaleString(loc->text, localeConstant, text);
1799 }
1800 }
1801
1802 draft = MailDraft(subject, text);
1803 }
1804
1805 SQLTransaction trans = CharacterDatabase.BeginTransaction();
1806
1807 Item* item = reward->itemId ? Item::CreateItem(reward->itemId, 1, GetOwner()) : NULL;
1808 if (item)
1809 {
1810 // save new item before send
1811 item->SaveToDB(trans); // save for prevent lost at next mail load, if send fail then item will deleted
1812
1813 // item
1814 draft.AddItem(item);
1815 }
1816
1817 draft.SendMailTo(trans, GetOwner(), MailSender(MAIL_CREATURE, uint64(reward->sender)));
1818 CharacterDatabase.CommitTransaction(trans);
1819 }
1820}
1821
1822template<>
1823void AchievementMgr<Guild>::CompletedAchievement(AchievementEntry const* achievement, Player* referencePlayer)
1824{
1825 TC_LOG_DEBUG("achievement", "AchievementMgr<Guild>::CompletedAchievement(%u)", achievement->ID);
1826
1827 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_COUNTER || HasAchieved(achievement->ID))
1828 return;
1829
1830 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_SHOW_IN_GUILD_NEWS)
1831 if (Guild* guild = referencePlayer->GetGuild())
1832 guild->AddGuildNews(GUILD_NEWS_GUILD_ACHIEVEMENT, ObjectGuid::Empty, achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_SHOW_IN_GUILD_HEADER, achievement->ID);
1833
1834 SendAchievementEarned(achievement);
1835 CompletedAchievementData& ca = m_completedAchievements[achievement->ID];
1836 ca.date = time(NULL);
1837 ca.changed = true;
1838
1839 if (achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_SHOW_GUILD_MEMBERS)
1840 {
1841 if (referencePlayer->GetGuildId() == GetOwner()->GetId())
1842 ca.guids.insert(referencePlayer->GetGUID());
1843
1844 if (Group const* group = referencePlayer->GetGroup())
1845 for (GroupReference const* ref = group->GetFirstMember(); ref != NULL; ref = ref->next())
1846 if (Player const* groupMember = ref->GetSource())
1847 if (groupMember->GetGuildId() == GetOwner()->GetId())
1848 ca.guids.insert(groupMember->GetGUID());
1849 }
1850
1851 sAchievementMgr->SetRealmCompleted(achievement, referencePlayer->GetInstanceId());
1852
1853 _achievementPoints += achievement->Points;
1854
1855 UpdateAchievementCriteria(ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_ACHIEVEMENT, 0, 0, 0, NULL, referencePlayer);
1856 UpdateAchievementCriteria(ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EARN_ACHIEVEMENT_POINTS, achievement->Points, 0, 0, NULL, referencePlayer);
1857}

1870template<class T>
1871void AchievementMgr<T>::SendAllAchievementData(Player* /*receiver*/) const
1872{
1873 VisibleAchievementCheck filterInvisible;
1874 WorldPackets::Achievement::AllAchievementData achievementData;
1875 achievementData.Data.Earned.reserve(m_completedAchievements.size());
1876 achievementData.Data.Progress.reserve(m_criteriaProgress.size());
1877
1878 for (auto itr = m_completedAchievements.begin(); itr != m_completedAchievements.end(); ++itr)
1879 {
1880 AchievementEntry const* achievement = filterInvisible(*itr);
1881 if (!achievement)
1882 continue;
1883
1884 WorldPackets::Achievement::EarnedAchievement earned;
1885 earned.Id = itr->first;
1886 earned.Date = itr->second.date;
1887 if (!(achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_ACCOUNT))
1888 {
1889 earned.Owner = GetOwner()->GetGUID();
1890 earned.VirtualRealmAddress = earned.NativeRealmAddress = GetVirtualRealmAddress();
1891 }
1892 achievementData.Data.Earned.push_back(earned);
1893 }
1894
1895 for (auto itr = m_criteriaProgress.begin(); itr != m_criteriaProgress.end(); ++itr)
1896 {
1897 WorldPackets::Achievement::CriteriaProgress progress;
1898 progress.Id = itr->first;
1899 progress.Quantity = itr->second.counter;
1900 progress.Player = itr->second.PlayerGUID;
1901 progress.Flags = 0;
1902 progress.Date = itr->second.date;
1903 progress.TimeFromStart = 0;
1904 progress.TimeFromCreate = 0;
1905 achievementData.Data.Progress.push_back(progress);
1906 }
1907
1908 SendPacket(achievementData.Write());
1909}

2002 });

2015template<class T>
2016bool AchievementMgr<T>::CanUpdateCriteria(AchievementCriteria const* criteria, AchievementCriteriaTreeList const* trees, uint64 miscValue1, uint64 miscValue2, uint64 miscValue3, Unit const* unit, Player* referencePlayer)
2017{
2018 if (DisableMgr::IsDisabledFor(DISABLE_TYPE_ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA, criteria->ID, NULL))
2019 {
2020 TC_LOG_TRACE("achievement", "CanUpdateCriteria: (Id: %u Type %s) Disabled",
2021 criteria->ID, AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(criteria->Entry->Type));
2022 return false;
2023 }
2024
2025 bool treeRequirementPassed = false;
2026 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : *trees)
2027 {
2028 if (HasAchieved(tree->Achievement->ID))
2029 {
2030 TC_LOG_TRACE("achievement", "CanUpdateCriteria: (Id: %u Type %s Achievement %u) Achievement already earned",
2031 criteria->ID, AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(criteria->Entry->Type), tree->Achievement->ID);
2032 continue;
2033 }
2034
2035 if (tree->Achievement->MapID != -1 && referencePlayer->GetMapId() != uint32(tree->Achievement->MapID))
2036 {
2037 TC_LOG_TRACE("achievement", "CanUpdateCriteria: (Id: %u Type %s Achievement %u) Wrong map",
2038 criteria->ID, AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(criteria->Entry->Type), tree->Achievement->ID);
2039 continue;
2040 }
2041
2042 if ((tree->Achievement->Faction == ACHIEVEMENT_FACTION_HORDE && referencePlayer->GetTeam() != HORDE) ||
2043 (tree->Achievement->Faction == ACHIEVEMENT_FACTION_ALLIANCE && referencePlayer->GetTeam() != ALLIANCE))
2044 {
2045 TC_LOG_TRACE("achievement", "CanUpdateCriteria: (Id: %u Type %s Achievement %u) Wrong faction",
2046 criteria->ID, AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(criteria->Entry->Type), tree->Achievement->ID);
2047 continue;
2048 }
2049
2050 treeRequirementPassed = true;
2051 break;
2052 }
2053
2054 if (!treeRequirementPassed)
2055 return false;
2056
2057 if (!RequirementsSatisfied(criteria, miscValue1, miscValue2, miscValue3, unit, referencePlayer))
2058 {
2059 TC_LOG_TRACE("achievement", "CanUpdateCriteria: (Id: %u Type %s) Requirements not satisfied",
2060 criteria->ID, AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(criteria->Entry->Type));
2061 return false;
2062 }
2063
2064 if (criteria->Modifier && !AdditionalRequirementsSatisfied(criteria->Modifier, miscValue1, miscValue2, unit, referencePlayer))
2065 {
2066 TC_LOG_TRACE("achievement", "CanUpdateCriteria: (Id: %u Type %s) Additional requirements not satisfied",
2067 criteria->ID, AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(criteria->Entry->Type));
2068 return false;
2069 }
2070
2071 if (!ConditionsSatisfied(criteria, referencePlayer))
2072 {
2073 TC_LOG_TRACE("achievement", "CanUpdateCriteria: (Id: %u Type %s) Conditions not satisfied",
2074 criteria->ID, AchievementGlobalMgr::GetCriteriaTypeString(criteria->Entry->Type));
2075 return false;
2076 }
2077
2078 return true;
2079}
2080
2081template<class T>
2082bool AchievementMgr<T>::ConditionsSatisfied(AchievementCriteria const* criteria, Player* referencePlayer) const
2083{
2084 if (!criteria->Entry->FailEvent)
2085 return true;
2086
2087 switch (criteria->Entry->FailEvent)
2088 {
2089 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_CONDITION_BG_MAP:
2090 if (!referencePlayer->InBattleground())
2091 return false;
2092 break;
2093 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_CONDITION_NOT_IN_GROUP:
2094 if (referencePlayer->GetGroup())
2095 return false;
2096 break;
2097 default:
2098 break;
2099 }
2100
2101 return true;
2102}
2103
2104template<class T>
2105bool AchievementMgr<T>::RequirementsSatisfied(AchievementCriteria const* achievementCriteria, uint64 miscValue1, uint64 miscValue2, uint64 miscValue3, Unit const* unit, Player* referencePlayer) const
2106{
2107 switch (AchievementCriteriaTypes(achievementCriteria->Entry->Type))
2108 {
2109 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ACCEPTED_SUMMONINGS:
2110 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_DAILY_QUEST:
2111 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CREATE_AUCTION:
2112 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_FALL_WITHOUT_DYING:
2113 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_FLIGHT_PATHS_TAKEN:

2129 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_MONEY_FROM_QUEST_REWARD:
2130 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_MONEY_FROM_VENDORS:
2131 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_NUMBER_OF_TALENT_RESETS:
2132 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_QUEST_ABANDONED:
2133 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_REACH_GUILD_LEVEL:
2134 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_GREED:
2135 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_NEED:
2136 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_SPECIAL_PVP_KILL:
2137 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_TOTAL_DAMAGE_RECEIVED:
2138 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_TOTAL_HEALING_RECEIVED:

2140 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_VISIT_BARBER_SHOP:

2142 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_RATED_ARENA:
2143 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WON_AUCTIONS:
2144 if (!miscValue1)
2145 return false;
2146 break;
2147 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BUY_BANK_SLOT:
2148 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_DAILY_QUEST_DAILY:
2149 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_QUEST_COUNT:
2150 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EARN_ACHIEVEMENT_POINTS:

2152 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_GAIN_HONORED_REPUTATION:
