2154 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HIGHEST_GOLD_VALUE_OWNED:
2155 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HIGHEST_PERSONAL_RATING:
2156 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KNOWN_FACTIONS:
2157 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_REACH_LEVEL:
2158 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ON_LOGIN:
2159 break;
2160 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_ACHIEVEMENT:
2161 if (m_completedAchievements.find(achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.AchievementID) == m_completedAchievements.end())
2162 return false;
2163 break;
2164 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_BG:
2165 if (!miscValue1 || achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.MapID != referencePlayer->GetMapId())
2166 return false;
2167 break;
2168 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KILL_CREATURE:
2169 if (!miscValue1 || achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.CreatureID != miscValue1)
2170 return false;
2171 break;
2172 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_REACH_SKILL_LEVEL:
2173 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LEARN_SKILL_LEVEL:
2174 // update at loading or specific skill update
2175 if (miscValue1 && miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.SkillID)
2176 return false;
2177 break;
2178 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_QUESTS_IN_ZONE:
2179 if (miscValue1 && miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.ZoneID)
2180 return false;
2181 break;
2182 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_BATTLEGROUND:
2183 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATH_AT_MAP:
2184 if (!miscValue1 || referencePlayer->GetMapId() != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.MapID)
2185 return false;
2186 break;
2187 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATH:
2188 {
2189 if (!miscValue1)
2190 return false;
2191 break;
2192 }
2193 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATH_IN_DUNGEON:
2194 {
2195 if (!miscValue1)
2196 return false;
2197
2198 Map const* map = referencePlayer->IsInWorld() ? referencePlayer->GetMap() : sMapMgr->FindMap(referencePlayer->GetMapId(), referencePlayer->GetInstanceId());
2199 if (!map || !map->IsDungeon())
2200 return false;
2201
2202 //FIXME: work only for instances where max == min for players
2203 if (map->ToInstanceMap()->GetMaxPlayers() != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.GroupSize)
2204 return false;
2205 break;
2206 }
2207 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KILLED_BY_CREATURE:
2208 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.CreatureID)
2209 return false;
2210 break;
2211 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_KILLED_BY_PLAYER:
2212 if (!miscValue1 || !unit || unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
2213 return false;
2214 break;
2215 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DEATHS_FROM:
2216 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue2 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.DamageType)
2217 return false;
2218 break;
2219 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_COMPLETE_QUEST:
2220 {
2221 // if miscValues != 0, it contains the questID.
2222 if (miscValue1)
2223 {
2224 if (miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.QuestID)
2225 return false;
2226 }
2227 else
2228 {
2229 // login case.
2230 if (!referencePlayer->GetQuestRewardStatus(achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.QuestID))
2231 return false;
2232 }
2233
2234 if (AchievementCriteriaDataSet const* data = sAchievementMgr->GetCriteriaDataSet(achievementCriteria))
2235 if (!data->Meets(referencePlayer, unit))
2236 return false;
2237 break;
2238 }
2239 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BE_SPELL_TARGET:
2240 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BE_SPELL_TARGET2:
2241 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CAST_SPELL:
2242 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CAST_SPELL2:
2243 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.SpellID)
2244 return false;
2245 break;
2246 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LEARN_SPELL:
2247 if (miscValue1 && miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.SpellID)
2248 return false;
2249
2250 if (!referencePlayer->HasSpell(achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.SpellID))
2251 return false;
2252 break;
2253 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LOOT_TYPE:
2254 // miscValue1 = itemId - miscValue2 = count of item loot
2255 // miscValue3 = loot_type (note: 0 = LOOT_CORPSE and then it ignored)
2256 if (!miscValue1 || !miscValue2 || !miscValue3 || miscValue3 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.LootType)
2257 return false;
2258 break;
2259 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_OWN_ITEM:
2260 if (miscValue1 && achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.ItemID != miscValue1)
2261 return false;
2262 break;
2263 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_USE_ITEM:
2264 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LOOT_ITEM:
2265 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EQUIP_ITEM:
2266 if (!miscValue1 || achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.ItemID != miscValue1)
2267 return false;
2268 break;
2269 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EXPLORE_AREA:
2270 {
2271 WorldMapOverlayEntry const* worldOverlayEntry = sWorldMapOverlayStore.LookupEntry(achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.WorldMapOverlayID);
2272 if (!worldOverlayEntry)
2273 break;
2274
2275 bool matchFound = false;
2276 for (int j = 0; j < MAX_WORLD_MAP_OVERLAY_AREA_IDX; ++j)
2277 {
2278 AreaTableEntry const* area = sAreaTableStore.LookupEntry(worldOverlayEntry->AreaID[j]);
2279 if (!area)
2280 break;
2281
2282 if (area->AreaBit < 0)
2283 continue;
2284
2285 uint32 playerIndexOffset = uint32(area->AreaBit) / 32;
2286 if (playerIndexOffset >= PLAYER_EXPLORED_ZONES_SIZE)
2287 continue;
2288
2289 uint32 mask = 1 << (uint32(area->AreaBit) % 32);
2290 if (referencePlayer->GetUInt32Value(PLAYER_EXPLORED_ZONES_1 + playerIndexOffset) & mask)
2291 {
2292 matchFound = true;
2293 break;
2294 }
2295 }
2296
2297 if (!matchFound)
2298 return false;
2299 break;
2300 }
2301 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_GAIN_REPUTATION:
2302 if (miscValue1 && miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.FactionID)
2303 return false;
2304 break;
2305 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_EQUIP_EPIC_ITEM:
2306 // miscValue1 = itemid miscValue2 = itemSlot
2307 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue2 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.ItemSlot)
2308 return false;
2309 break;
2310 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_NEED_ON_LOOT:
2311 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_ROLL_GREED_ON_LOOT:
2312 {
2313 // miscValue1 = itemid miscValue2 = diced value
2314 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue2 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.RollValue)
2315 return false;
2316
2317 ItemTemplate const* proto = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(uint32(miscValue1));
2318 if (!proto)
2319 return false;
2320 break;
2321 }
2322 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DO_EMOTE:
2323 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.EmoteID)
2324 return false;
2325 break;
2326 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_DAMAGE_DONE:
2327 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HEALING_DONE:
2328 if (!miscValue1)
2329 return false;
2330
2331 if (achievementCriteria->Entry->FailEvent == ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_CONDITION_BG_MAP)
2332 {
2333 if (!referencePlayer->InBattleground())
2334 return false;
2335
2336 // map specific case (BG in fact) expected player targeted damage/heal
2337 if (!unit || unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
2338 return false;
2339 }
2340 break;
2341 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_USE_GAMEOBJECT:
2342 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_FISH_IN_GAMEOBJECT:
2343 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.GameObjectID)
2344 return false;
2345 break;
2346 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LEARN_SKILLLINE_SPELLS:
2347 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LEARN_SKILL_LINE:
2348 if (miscValue1 && miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.SkillID)
2349 return false;
2350 break;
2351 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_LOOT_EPIC_ITEM:
2352 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_RECEIVE_EPIC_ITEM:
2353 {
2354 if (!miscValue1)
2355 return false;
2356 ItemTemplate const* proto = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(uint32(miscValue1));
2357 if (!proto || proto->GetQuality() < ITEM_QUALITY_EPIC)
2358 return false;
2359 break;
2360 }
2361 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HK_CLASS:
2362 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.ClassID)
2363 return false;
2364 break;
2365 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HK_RACE:
2366 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.RaceID)
2367 return false;
2368 break;
2369 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_BG_OBJECTIVE_CAPTURE:
2370 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.ObjectiveId)
2371 return false;
2372 break;
2373 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HONORABLE_KILL_AT_AREA:
2374 if (!miscValue1 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.AreaID)
2375 return false;
2376 break;
2377 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_CURRENCY:
2378 if (!miscValue1 || !miscValue2 || int64(miscValue2) < 0
2379 || miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.CurrencyID)
2380 return false;
2381 break;
2382 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_WIN_ARENA:
2383 if (miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.MapID)
2384 return false;
2385 break;
2386 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_HIGHEST_TEAM_RATING:
2387 return false;
2388 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_TYPE_PLACE_GARRISON_BUILDING:
2389 if (miscValue1 != achievementCriteria->Entry->Asset.GarrBuildingID)
2390 return false;
2391 break;
2392 default:
2393 break;
2394 }
2395 return true;
2396}
2397
2398template<class T>
2399bool AchievementMgr<T>::AdditionalRequirementsSatisfied(ModifierTreeNode const* tree, uint64 miscValue1, uint64 miscValue2, Unit const* unit, Player* referencePlayer) const
2400{
2401 for (ModifierTreeNode const* node : tree->Children)
2402 if (!AdditionalRequirementsSatisfied(node, miscValue1, miscValue2, unit, referencePlayer))
2403 return false;
2404
2405 uint32 reqType = tree->Entry->Type;
2406 if (!reqType)
2407 return true;
2408
2409 uint32 reqValue = tree->Entry->Asset[0];
2410
2411 switch (AchievementCriteriaAdditionalCondition(reqType))
2412 {
2413 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_CREATURE_ENTRY: // 4
2414 if (!unit || unit->GetEntry() != reqValue)
2415 return false;
2416 break;
2417 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_MUST_BE_PLAYER: // 5
2418 if (!unit || unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
2419 return false;
2420 break;
2421 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_MUST_BE_DEAD: // 6
2422 if (!unit || unit->IsAlive())
2423 return false;
2424 break;
2425 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_MUST_BE_ENEMY: // 7
2426 if (!unit || !referencePlayer->IsHostileTo(unit))
2427 return false;
2428 break;
2429 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_SOURCE_HAS_AURA: // 8
2430 if (!referencePlayer->HasAura(reqValue))
2431 return false;
2432 break;
2433 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_HAS_AURA: // 10
2434 if (!unit || !unit->HasAura(reqValue))
2435 return false;
2436 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_HAS_AURA_TYPE: // 11
2437 if (!unit || !unit->HasAuraType(AuraType(reqValue)))
2438 return false;
2439 break;
2440 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_ITEM_QUALITY_MIN: // 14
2441 {
2442 // miscValue1 is itemid
2443 ItemTemplate const* const item = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(uint32(miscValue1));
2444 if (!item || item->GetQuality() < reqValue)
2445 return false;
2446 break;
2447 }
2448 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_ITEM_QUALITY_EQUALS: // 15
2449 {
2450 // miscValue1 is itemid
2451 ItemTemplate const* const item = sObjectMgr->GetItemTemplate(uint32(miscValue1));
2452 if (!item || item->GetQuality() != reqValue)
2453 return false;
2454 break;
2455 }
2456 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_SOURCE_AREA_OR_ZONE: // 17
2457 {
2458 uint32 zoneId, areaId;
2459 referencePlayer->GetZoneAndAreaId(zoneId, areaId);
2460 if (zoneId != reqValue && areaId != reqValue)
2461 return false;
2462 break;
2463 }
2464 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_AREA_OR_ZONE: // 18
2465 {
2466 if (!unit)
2467 return false;
2468 uint32 zoneId, areaId;
2469 unit->GetZoneAndAreaId(zoneId, areaId);
2470 if (zoneId != reqValue && areaId != reqValue)
2471 return false;
2472 break;
2473 }
2474 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_MAP_DIFFICULTY: // 20
2475 if (uint32(referencePlayer->GetMap()->GetDifficultyID()) != reqValue)
2476 return false;
2477 break;
2478 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_ARENA_TYPE:
2479 {
2480 Battleground* bg = referencePlayer->GetBattleground();
2481 if (!bg || !bg->isArena() || bg->GetArenaType() != reqValue)
2482 return false;
2483 break;
2484 }
2485 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_SOURCE_RACE: // 25
2486 if (referencePlayer->getRace() != reqValue)
2487 return false;
2488 break;
2489 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_SOURCE_CLASS: // 26
2490 if (referencePlayer->getClass() != reqValue)
2491 return false;
2492 break;
2493 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_RACE: // 27
2494 if (!unit || unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || unit->getRace() != reqValue)
2495 return false;
2496 break;
2497 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_CLASS: // 28
2498 if (!unit || unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || unit->getClass() != reqValue)
2499 return false;
2500 break;
2501 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_MAX_GROUP_MEMBERS: // 29
2502 if (referencePlayer->GetGroup() && referencePlayer->GetGroup()->GetMembersCount() >= reqValue)
2503 return false;
2504 break;
2505 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_CREATURE_TYPE: // 30
2506 {
2507 if (!unit)
2508 return false;
2509 Creature const* const creature = unit->ToCreature();
2510 if (!creature || creature->GetCreatureType() != reqValue)
2511 return false;
2512 break;
2513 }
2514 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_SOURCE_MAP: // 32
2515 if (referencePlayer->GetMapId() != reqValue)
2516 return false;
2517 break;
2518 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TITLE_BIT_INDEX: // 38
2519 // miscValue1 is title's bit index
2520 if (miscValue1 != reqValue)
2521 return false;
2522 break;
2523 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_SOURCE_LEVEL: // 39
2524 if (referencePlayer->getLevel() != reqValue)
2525 return false;
2526 break;
2527 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_LEVEL: // 40
2528 if (!unit || unit->getLevel() != reqValue)
2529 return false;
2530 break;
2531 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_ZONE: // 41
2532 if (!unit || unit->GetZoneId() != reqValue)
2533 return false;
2534 break;
2535 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_TARGET_HEALTH_PERCENT_BELOW: // 46
2536 if (!unit || unit->GetHealthPct() >= reqValue)
2537 return false;
2538 break;
2539 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_BATTLE_PET_SPECIES: // 91
2540 if (miscValue1 != reqValue)
2541 return false;
2542 break;
2543 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_GARRISON_FOLLOWER_QUALITY: // 145
2544 {
2545 if (!referencePlayer)
2546 return false;
2547 Garrison* garrison = referencePlayer->GetGarrison();
2548 if (!garrison)
2549 return false;
2550 Garrison::Follower const* follower = garrison->GetFollower(miscValue1);
2551 if (!follower || follower->PacketInfo.Quality != reqValue)
2552 return false;
2553
2554 break;
2555 }
2556 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_GARRISON_FOLLOWER_LEVEL: // 146
2557 {
2558 if (!referencePlayer)
2559 return false;
2560 Garrison* garrison = referencePlayer->GetGarrison();
2561 if (!garrison)
2562 return false;
2563 Garrison::Follower const* follower = garrison->GetFollower(miscValue1);
2564 if (!follower || follower->PacketInfo.FollowerLevel < reqValue)
2565 return false;
2566
2567 break;
2568 }
2569 case ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_ADDITIONAL_CONDITION_GARRISON_FOLLOWER_ILVL: // 184
2570 {
2571 if (!referencePlayer)
2572 return false;
2573 Garrison* garrison = referencePlayer->GetGarrison();
2574 if (!garrison)
2575 return false;
2576 Garrison::Follower const* follower = garrison->GetFollower(miscValue1);
2577 if (!follower || follower->GetItemLevel() < reqValue)
2578 return false;
2579 break;
2580 }
2581 default:
2582 break;
2583 }
2584 return true;
2585}

2895{
2896 for (AchievementCriteriaTreeMap::iterator itr = _achievementCriteriaTrees.begin(); itr != _achievementCriteriaTrees.end(); ++itr)
2897 delete itr->second;

2900 delete itr->second;

2906void AchievementGlobalMgr::LoadAchievementCriteriaModifiersTree()
2907{
2908 uint32 oldMSTime = getMSTime();
2909
2910 if (sModifierTreeStore.GetNumRows() == 0)
2911 {
2912 TC_LOG_ERROR("server.loading", ">> Loaded 0 achievement criteria modifiers.");
2913 return;
2914 }
2915
2916 // Load modifier tree nodes
2917 for (uint32 i = 0; i < sModifierTreeStore.GetNumRows(); ++i)
2918 {
2919 ModifierTreeEntry const* tree = sModifierTreeStore.LookupEntry(i);
2920 if (!tree)
2921 continue;
2922
2923 ModifierTreeNode* node = new ModifierTreeNode();
2924 node->Entry = tree;
2925 _criteriaModifiers[node->Entry->ID] = node;
2926 }
2927
2928 // Build tree
2929 for (auto itr = _criteriaModifiers.begin(); itr != _criteriaModifiers.end(); ++itr)
2930 {
2931 if (!itr->second->Entry->Parent)
2932 continue;
2933
2934 auto parent = _criteriaModifiers.find(itr->second->Entry->Parent);
2935 if (parent != _criteriaModifiers.end())
2936 parent->second->Children.push_back(itr->second);
2937 }
2938
2939 TC_LOG_INFO("server.loading", ">> Loaded %u achievement criteria modifiers in %u ms", uint32(_criteriaModifiers.size()), GetMSTimeDiffToNow(oldMSTime));
2940}
2941
2942void AchievementGlobalMgr::LoadAchievementCriteriaList()
2943{
2944 uint32 oldMSTime = getMSTime();
2945
2946 if (sCriteriaTreeStore.GetNumRows() == 0)
2947 {
2948 TC_LOG_ERROR("server.loading", ">> Loaded 0 achievement criteria.");
2949 return;
2950 }
2951
2952 std::unordered_map<uint32 /*criteriaTreeID*/, AchievementEntry const*> achievementCriteriaTreeIds;
2953 for (uint32 i = 0; i < sAchievementStore.GetNumRows(); ++i)
2954 if (AchievementEntry const* achievement = sAchievementStore.LookupEntry(i))
2955 if (achievement->CriteriaTree)
2956 achievementCriteriaTreeIds[achievement->CriteriaTree] = achievement;
2957
2958 // Load criteria tree nodes
2959 for (uint32 i = 0; i < sCriteriaTreeStore.GetNumRows(); ++i)
2960 {
2961 CriteriaTreeEntry const* tree = sCriteriaTreeStore.LookupEntry(i);
2962 if (!tree)
2963 continue;
2964
2965 // Find linked achievement
2966 auto achievementItr = achievementCriteriaTreeIds.find(tree->ID);
2967 CriteriaTreeEntry const* cur = tree;
2968 while (achievementItr == achievementCriteriaTreeIds.end())
2969 {
2970 if (!cur->Parent)
2971 break;
2972
2973 cur = sCriteriaTreeStore.LookupEntry(cur->Parent);
2974 if (!cur)
2975 break;
2976
2977 achievementItr = achievementCriteriaTreeIds.find(cur->ID);
2978 }
2979
2980 if (achievementItr == achievementCriteriaTreeIds.end())
2981 continue;
2982
2983 AchievementCriteriaTree* achievementCriteriaTree = new AchievementCriteriaTree();
2984 achievementCriteriaTree->ID = i;
2985 achievementCriteriaTree->Achievement = achievementItr->second;
2986 achievementCriteriaTree->Entry = tree;
2987
2988 _achievementCriteriaTrees[achievementCriteriaTree->Entry->ID] = achievementCriteriaTree;
2989 }
2990
2991 // Build tree
2992 for (auto itr = _achievementCriteriaTrees.begin(); itr != _achievementCriteriaTrees.end(); ++itr)
2993 {
2994 if (!itr->second->Entry->Parent)
2995 continue;
2996
2997 auto parent = _achievementCriteriaTrees.find(itr->second->Entry->Parent);
2998 if (parent != _achievementCriteriaTrees.end())
2999 {
3000 parent->second->Children.push_back(itr->second);
3001 while (parent != _achievementCriteriaTrees.end())
3002 {
3003 auto cur = parent;
3004 parent = _achievementCriteriaTrees.find(parent->second->Entry->Parent);
3005 if (parent == _achievementCriteriaTrees.end())
3006 {
3007 if (sCriteriaStore.LookupEntry(itr->second->Entry->CriteriaID))
3008 _achievementCriteriaTreeByCriteria[itr->second->Entry->CriteriaID].push_back(cur->second);
3009 }
3010 }
3011 }
3012 else if (sCriteriaStore.LookupEntry(itr->second->Entry->CriteriaID))
3013 _achievementCriteriaTreeByCriteria[itr->second->Entry->CriteriaID].push_back(itr->second);
3014 }
3015
3016 // Load criteria
3017 uint32 criterias = 0;
3018 uint32 guildCriterias = 0;
3019 for (uint32 i = 0; i < sCriteriaStore.GetNumRows(); ++i)
3020 {
3021 CriteriaEntry const* criteria = sCriteriaStore.LookupEntry(i);
3022 if (!criteria)
3023 continue;
3024
3025 auto treeItr = _achievementCriteriaTreeByCriteria.find(i);
3026 if (treeItr == _achievementCriteriaTreeByCriteria.end())
3027 continue;
3028
3029 AchievementCriteria* achievementCriteria = new AchievementCriteria();
3030 achievementCriteria->ID = i;
3031 achievementCriteria->Entry = criteria;
3032 auto mod = _criteriaModifiers.find(criteria->ModifierTreeId);
3033 if (mod != _criteriaModifiers.end())
3034 achievementCriteria->Modifier = mod->second;
3035
3036 _achievementCriteria[achievementCriteria->ID] = achievementCriteria;
3037
3038 for (AchievementCriteriaTree const* tree : treeItr->second)
3039 {
3040 if (tree->Achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_GUILD)
3041 achievementCriteria->FlagsCu |= ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_FLAG_CU_GUILD;
3042 else if (tree->Achievement->Flags & ACHIEVEMENT_FLAG_ACCOUNT)
3043 achievementCriteria->FlagsCu |= ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_FLAG_CU_ACCOUNT;
3044 else
3045 achievementCriteria->FlagsCu |= ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_FLAG_CU_PLAYER;
3046 }
3047
3048 if (achievementCriteria->FlagsCu & ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_FLAG_CU_GUILD)
3049 {
3050 ++guildCriterias;
3051 _guildAchievementCriteriasByType[criteria->Type].push_back(achievementCriteria);
3052 }
3053
3054 if (achievementCriteria->FlagsCu & (ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_FLAG_CU_PLAYER | ACHIEVEMENT_CRITERIA_FLAG_CU_ACCOUNT))
3055 {
3056 ++criterias;
3057 _achievementCriteriasByType[criteria->Type].push_back(achievementCriteria);
3058 }
3059
3060 if (criteria->StartTimer)
3061 _achievementCriteriasByTimedType[criteria->StartEvent].push_back(achievementCriteria);
3062 }
3063
3064 for (auto& p : _achievementCriteriaTrees)
3065 const_cast<AchievementCriteriaTree*>(p.second)->Criteria = GetAchievementCriteria(p.second->Entry->CriteriaID);
3066
3067 TC_LOG_INFO("server.loading", ">> Loaded %u achievement criteria and %u guild achievement crieteria in %u ms", criterias, guildCriterias, GetMSTimeDiffToNow(oldMSTime));
3068}
3069
3070void AchievementGlobalMgr::LoadAchievementReferenceList()
3071{
3072 uint32 oldMSTime = getMSTime();
3073
3074 if (sAchievementStore.GetNumRows() == 0)
3075 {
3076 TC_LOG_INFO("server.loading", ">> Loaded 0 achievement references.");
3077 return;
3078 }
3079
3080 uint32 count = 0;
3081
3082 for (uint32 entryId = 0; entryId < sAchievementStore.GetNumRows(); ++entryId)
3083 {
3084 AchievementEntry const* achievement = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievement(entryId);
3085 if (!achievement || !achievement->SharesCriteria)
3086 continue;
3087
3088 _achievementListByReferencedId[achievement->SharesCriteria].push_back(achievement);
3089 ++count;
3090 }
3091
3092 // Once Bitten, Twice Shy (10 player) - Icecrown Citadel
3093 if (AchievementEntry const* achievement = sAchievementMgr->GetAchievement(4539))
3094 const_cast<AchievementEntry*>(achievement)->MapID = 631; // Correct map requirement (currently has Ulduar); 6.0.3 note - it STILL has ulduar requirement
3095
3096 TC_LOG_INFO("server.loading", ">> Loaded %u achievement references in %u ms", count, GetMSTimeDiffToNow(oldMSTime));
3097}
3098
3099void AchievementGlobalMgr::LoadAchievementCriteriaData()
3100{
3101 uint32 oldMSTime = getMSTime();
3102
3103 _criteriaDataMap.clear(); // need for reload case
3104
3105 QueryResult result = WorldDatabase.Query("SELECT criteria_id, type, value1, value2, ScriptName FROM achievement_criteria_data");
3106
3107 if (!result)
3108 {
3109 TC_LOG_INFO("server.loading", ">> Loaded 0 additional achievement criteria data. DB table `achievement_criteria_data` is empty.");
3110 return;
3111 }
3112
3113 uint32 count = 0;
3114
3115 do
3116 {

3260 reward.titleId[1] = 0;
